properties.AssetSummary: Zydeco: Provides a critical outlet to alleviate current transportation bottlenecks of crude oil arriving in Houston, TX from the Eagle Ford shale, Permian Basin and Bakken shale. Connects to several crude oil pipeline in Houston and Port Neches/Nederland areas. Spans over 350 miles and has a mainline capacity of 375 kbpd.
